<H1><A NAME=SECTION00060000000000000000>3 Special Features</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME=special>&#160;</A> <A NAME=111>&#160;</A>
This section describes some special features of the translator which
can be considered as <em> hypertext extensions to LaTeX</em>.
These are implemented as new LaTeX commands which have special 
meaning during the translation to HTML but are mostly ignored when
processed by LaTeX.
<P>
<A NAME=113>&#160;</A>
All the new commands used in the sections 
below are defined in the file <A HREF="http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/doc/html.sty.txt"><tt> html.sty</tt></A> which is part of the 
distribution. <em> This file must be included in any 
LaTeX document using these features</em><A NAME=tex2html15 HREF="footnode.html#965"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="http://wolf2.mpibpc.gwdg.de/icons/foot_motif.gif"></A>.
<P>
