<B>Up:</B> <A NAME=tex2html445 HREF="manual.html">The LaTeX2HTML Translator</A>
<B> Previous:</B> <A NAME=tex2html439 HREF="node23.html">3.11 FiguresTables and </A>
<BR> <HR> <P>
<H1><A NAME=SECTION00070000000000000000>4 Getting LaTeX2HTML</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME=349>&#160;</A>
The <A HREF="http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/latex2html.tar">source code can be obtained 
at http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/latex2html.tar.</A>
or <A HREF="http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/latex2html.tar-gz">as a compressed archive at http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/latex2html.tar-gz</A>
The source code is also available 
via anonymous FTP at 
<A HREF="ftp://ftp.tex.ac.uk/pub/archive/support/latex2html">ftp://ftp.tex.ac.uk/pub/archive/support/latex2html</A>
or
<A HREF="ftp://sunsite.unc.edu/pub/packages/infosystems/WWW/tools/translators/latex2html">ftp://sunsite.unc.edu/pub/packages/infosystems/WWW/tools/translators/latex2html</A>.
Other FTP sites nearer to you can be found using <tt> Archie</tt>
at
<A HREF="http://hoohoo.ncsa.uiuc.edu/archie.html">http://hoohoo.ncsa.uiuc.edu/archie.html</A>
or 
<A HREF="http://www.pvv.unit.no/archie/">http://www.pvv.unit.no/archie/</A>
(faster).
<P>
<b> Warning:</b> Some FTP sites may not carry the latest version.
<P>
Updates and patches are posted on the <b> LaTeX</b>2<tt>HTML</tt>  server at
<A HREF="http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/doc/latex2html/latex2html.html">http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/doc/latex2html/latex2html.html</A>
<P>
If you get the <tt> tar</tt> version, save it into a file, say <tt> latex2html.tar</tt>
and then extract the files with 
<PRE>% tar xvf latex2html.tar
</PRE>
<P>
You should then have the following:
<UL><LI> A <tt> README</tt> file.
<LI> A <tt> Changes</tt> file.
<LI> The <tt> latex2html</tt> Perl program.
<LI> A <A NAME=374>&#160;</A> <tt> texexpand</tt> Perl program <A NAME=tex2html41 HREF="footnode.html#376"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="http://wolf2.mpibpc.gwdg.de/icons/foot_motif.gif"></A>.
<LI> A <tt> latex2html.config</tt> configuration file.
<LI> An <tt> install-test</tt> installation and testing Perl script.
<LI> A <tt> dot.latex2html-init</tt> sample initialization file.
<LI> A <tt> html.sty</tt> style file.
<LI> A <tt> pstogif</tt> perl script.
<LI> Two <tt> pstoppm.ps</tt> files.
<LI> A <tt> docs/</tt> subdirectory containing a version of this
manual.
<LI> An <tt> icons/</tt> subdirectory containing various icons.
<LI> A <tt> styles/</tt> subdirectory containing Perl code for handling
some style files.
</UL><BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Arndt Koester <BR>
Fri May 12 14:23:56 MESZ 1995</I>
</ADDRESS>
