<H1><A NAME=SECTION000100000000000000000>7 Changes from Previous Versions</A></H1>
<P>
The <A HREF="http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/previous-versions">previous versions of the
translator and some patches</A>
are available. A <A HREF="http://cbl.leeds.ac.uk/nikos/tex2html/doc/Changes.txt">detailed list of changes</A>
which includes full credits to all who have contributed 
bug fixes or other code is also available with the
<b> LaTeX</b>2<tt>HTML</tt>  distribution in the file <tt> Changes</tt>.
