<H2><A NAME=SECTION000104000000000000000>7.4 Changes upto v0.5.1</A></H2>
<P>
<DL ><DT><b> Navigation Panel</b>
<DD>
The <A HREF="node18.html#secnavpanel">navigation panel</A>
is now fully configurable and much better looking.
<DT><b> Automatic Signatures</b>
<DD>
The signatures at the bottom of each page are now constructed
using <tt> nslookup</tt> (Thanks to Alberto Accomazzi
<b>&lt;</b>alberto@cfa.harvard.edu<b>&gt;</b>)
<DT><b> Numerous fixes including...</b>
<DD> 
<UL><LI> ``dead'' <tt> next_page</tt> buttons when the <tt> -split</tt> option
was used, and
<LI> internal <b> LaTeX</b>2<tt>HTML</tt>  markers appearing in section titles.
</UL> 
 </DL><BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Arndt Koester <BR>
Fri May 12 14:23:56 MESZ 1995</I>
