<BR> <HR> <P>
<H2><A NAME=SECTION000106000000000000000>7.6 Changes upto v0.3.1</A></H2>
<P>
These changes are mostly due to patches contributed by Robert S. Thau
<b>&lt;</b>rst@ai.mit.edu<b>&gt;</b>:
<UL><LI> Nested environments with the same name are now dealt with
properly.
<LI> Commands that are passed to LaTeX for processing which have 
environments in their arguments (e.g. a <tt> parbox</tt> command which 
an <tt> itemize</tt> environment as an argument) are now
processed correctly. A general mechanism for users to 
specify the syntax of commands that should be passed to LaTeX 
is described in Page <A HREF="node10.html#pass"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="http://wolf2.mpibpc.gwdg.de/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A>.
<LI> Fixed a problem with recognizing the <tt> special</tt> command.
<LI> Fixed bug in the generation of the index.
</UL><BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Arndt Koester <BR>
Fri May 12 14:23:56 MESZ 1995</I>
