<H2><A NAME=SECTION000108000000000000000>7.8 Changes upto v0.2</A></H2>
<P>
<UL><LI> Added a command line option
to switch off the navigation links
at the top of each page.
<LI> The navigation icons are now part of the distribution.
<LI> Added a customizable separator between the main body of the text
in a page and the child links from that page.
<LI> The order of the navigation keywords at the top of each page is
the same as that of the navigation icons.
<LI> The arguments of <tt> verbatim</tt> environments are now translated
into fixed width fonts.
<LI> A warning is given if a <tt> bbl</tt> (bibliography) file is 
needed but not found.
<LI> The installation is now (mostly) done by setting variables in 
just one file.
<LI> The <tt> pstoxbm</tt> script now uses environment variables
set in the initialization file.
<LI> Fixed bug in translating sequences of special HTML characters
(e.g. &amp;, <b>&lt;</b>, etc.)
<LI> Fixed bug in the handling of the <code>$$</code>-form of the dislay
math environment.
<LI> Fixed bug in the handling of the *-forms of environments.
<LI> Added sections on how to embed hyperlinks in a LaTeX document 
(see Page <A HREF="node12.html#sechyper"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="http://wolf2.mpibpc.gwdg.de/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A>) and on how to extend the translator
(see Page <A HREF="node7.html#secextend"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="http://wolf2.mpibpc.gwdg.de/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A>) in the documentation.
</UL><BR> <HR>
