<p>This section describes parameters in the CHARMM empirical
energy function.

<dl>
<dt><a href="#overview">Overview</a>
<dd>Overview of CHARMM parameter file by A. D. Mackerell Jr.
<dt><a href="#multiple">Multiple</a>
<dd>Rules for the use of multiple dihedrals in CHARMM22
