<TITLE>Low Impact</TITLE>
<H1><IMG SRC="icon.gif"> Low Impact</H1>

<HR> <P>


<UL>
<LI> Designed to be a small, fast server. <P>

Has a low impact on system resources, allowing it to serve documents
to a large number of users simultaneously with little slowdown. With
the amount of traffic <CODE>www.ncsa.uiuc.edu</CODE> gets, this was
required. <P>

<LI> Runs standalone, for faster performance, or under
     <CODE>inetd</CODE>. <P>

</UL>

<HR> <P>

