<DOCOLDNO>IA014-000148-B014-143</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://wolf2.mpibpc.gwdg.de:80/cgi/overview.html 134.76.213.25 19970217105608 text/html 2941
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 17 Feb 1997 10:56:27 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4.2
