<b>Healthbeat</b> features the latest information on important medical 
issues. Healthbeat airs Monday through Friday at 5pm on NewsCenter4.<p>

And on First 4 News, Pam Moore brings you the day's <b>Miracles of Medicine.</b> Miracles of Medicine airs Monday
through Friday at 4:00pm.

