hspace=4 vspace=0>



<b>Who's Hiring</b>  supplies job seekers with updated listings

of

employment

opportunities in the San Francisco Bay Area . Barring any

late-breaking

news

stories, the Who's Hiring segment airs Thursdays during the 5

o'clock

news on

KRON-TV Channel 4.<p>



For job seekers, call the Who's Hiring Job Hotline at (415)

561-8923

for a

recording of the current week's jobs.



<br clear=left>



<hr>



<b>For employers who would like to <b>list job openings, scroll to the bottom of this page

for more

information or call the Who's Hiring information line at (415) 561-8108.</b>



