<hr>

<blockquote>







<B>If you are an employer who would like to list your job

openings on Who's

Hiring, call (415) 561-8108. You may also send an e-mail to <a

href="mailto:whoshiring@kron.com">whoshiring@kron.com</a> or a fax to (415) 561-8742 with

the following

information:</B>



<OL>

<B><LI></B>  One sentence description of your company.<P>

<B><LI></B>  Number of positions available.<P>

<B><LI></B>  Types of positions. You may want to divide the

positions

into 4-5 categories

for easy reference.<P>

<B><LI></B>  Add general prerequisites (education/experience)

for each

category.<P>

<B><LI></B>  How would you like prospective employees to apply?

Via

in-person, mail, fax,

e-mail, phone interview?<P>

<B><LI></B>  Let us know if corporate video is available.<P>

<B><LI></B>  Does your company have a job hotline which lists

your

openings?<P>

<B><LI></B>  Is there a company Web site?<P>

</OL>



</blockquote>







