A state-supported program, Experience Unlimited is a no fee, public service volunteer

organization of professional, managerial, and technical career-seekers. Experience

Unlimited provides a supportive environment with job search resources and skill-enhancing

workshops.  For further information and to register for the next orientation meeting, call

9415) 771-1776 or stop by Experience Unlimited.<p>



