<h1>
Talk to NewsCenter4
</h1>
</center>
<center>[ <a href="#followups">Follow Ups</a> ] [ <a href="#postfp">Post Followup</a> ] [ <a href="http://www.kron.com/nc4/talk_to_nc4/talk2nc4.html">Return to Talk to NC4</a> ]</center>
<hr><p>
Posted by <a href="mailto:Rtowns@pacbell.net">Rtowns</a> on January 21, 1997 at 11:52:36:<p>
I do not believe that the O.J. Simpson re-trial diserves the continuing coverage that it is given by your channel and other television media.  It is no longer news.  There have been many oter murders and many other trials over the years that the media has been fixated on O.J. Simpson.  Most people do not care what happems in the re-trial.  Most people question the media interest.  Many wonder about the media ability to make news when there is no news - to tell the public what it should be interested in.
<br>
<br><hr><p>
<a name="followups">Follow Ups:</a><br>
<ul><!--insert: 5231-->
</ul><!--end: 5231-->
<br><hr><p>
