Posted by <a href="mailto:luce@apple.com">Kristin Luce</a> on January 21, 1997 at 11:27:44:<p>
Hello- You ran a story on the 11 o'clock news last Friday about a man named Rick Haddix, whose house in Yuba County was demolished because they needed to widen the levy there. I think I may have known that man 20 years ago, when I was growing up in Sacramento, and if so, I'd like to get in touch with him. Is there any way you can help me?
