I have read the previous messages regarding the congestion on AOL. I have been a subscriber since Oct. 1996, and although I, too, have a difficult time logging on at times, I find it to be a fantastic service, have gotten alot of usefull information from it and have made NUMEROUS friends online at AOL. I hope everyone will understand that life is not perfect and that you have to roll with the punches to get to the good stuff. Just something to think about.
