Posted by Marsha on January 19, 1997 at 09:38:41:<p>
For many years, I have turned away from CBS's Sunday Morning at 8:00 on Sunday mornings to watch Isabel and the news.  I have been irritated by Henry  and his nervous titterings. Generally,  I  read the newpaper while he babbles, but this morning, I couldn't take any more, so I turned on ABC's Sunday morning and really enojoyed it.  I was also delighted to find a local news program at 9:00 am that presents information in a calm manner.  I will miss Isabel, but that's all!  Thanks, Henry, for chasing me away.
