<!-----------------------Begin Profile --------------------------->
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<FONT SIZE=+2><b>DENNIS O'DONNELL</b></font><br>
<b>Senior Sports Producer</b><p>

Dennis O'Donnell joined KRON in 1982 where he is the senior member of the sport's team.  Since his arrival at KRON, his contributions helped earn the station  the honor of  "The Best Sports Cast in California" by the Associated Press  on five separate occasions.<P>

O'Donnell produces KRON's "NewsCenter 4 at 6" sportcasts and "Sitdown with Gary Radnich" sports specials.  He also anchors Bay TV's "Chalk  Talk," and pinch-hits for Gary Radnich as sports anchor at KRON.<P>

Along with his work at KRON, O'Donnell has anchored sports with KOVR in Sacramento and KFTY in Santa Rosa.  He has also called basketball and football play-by-play for Marin's Viacom Cable.<P>

