Posted by Chris on January 17, 1997 at 08:25:05:<p>
In Reply to: <a href="530.html">Stop crying Bill!!!!!</a> posted by Carlo on January 17, 1997 at 00:39:20:<p>
Listen Carlo, if you want to take a bottom line approach on this then yeah the decision is a no brainer. Anyone in the business would have done the same thing. I am only saying that it is still a crappy deal for the kids and the University. Honestly I would have had to take the job also but I would have at least tried to wait until the recruiting season was over. What difference does a couple of weeks make. He obviously was their #1 choice all along, so much that they pushed Seifert out to make room for him, so why not wait for Feb 7 to come and go. I am sure if Eddie D and Carmen wanted him that bad they could of kept it quiet for a few weeks. I guess all the preaching about commitment was abunch of bull and that all underclassmen should turn pro and help their families whatever. From a financail stanpoint hey you are the man, from the sporting standpoint you don't know jack. This is a bad move by the 49ers as you will soon see.<br>
<br>
